                    android:text="dsçjd sçldkfg sçdlfkjçlks;j dçfljçslkdjfçlk jsçldjfçkljsçdkl jfçkl sjçdlk fjçskl jçd fklj çgsk;ldjf kjs dçlfkjçdgskljf çklgjdsçlfkj ;lj" />
            </LinearLayout>
